name: The One You Feed
description:
Hey! This is for all y'all.  I'm still new here, a bit overwhelmed and blown away by the vast myriad of talent and palpable love flowing through this community. While I typically like to get lost in solitude and tinkering I'd like to improve on engagement and remember to share the love because
1: You all are a bunch of cool mofos
2: You're going to bring out the best in me.
3: I hope to do the same to some of you.

It may work against me to play with different methods and styles but that's what keeps it fun for me.  Maybe my own voice will come through regardless.

  I'll leave it at that for now so I can just mint that damn thing.  Godspeed.
Love, Mojo (Jason)

PS.Specifically to H=N, I'm amazed at what a lot of you are doing with the interactive aspect all within the limits of what can be uploaded (ZIP). WOW!!!
